Jack Pearl https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Pearl 0 Jack Pearl, born Jack Perlman (October 29, 1894 – December 25, 1982), was a vaudeville performer and a star of early radio. He was best known for his character Baron Munchausen. Jack_Pearl , born Jack_Perlman ( October_29_,_1894 – December_25_,_1982 ) , was a_vaudeville_performer and a_star of early_radio .
